    <h2 id="fmod-integration">
      Fmod Integration
    </h2>

  <p>
    All the sounds were integrated using Fmod.
<br>The most tricky part was the music which is semi-random.
<br>The composition is divided into a few loops which are played one after the other following rules, and playing a "Pause" track every X loops played.
  </p>

