                    <p><img src="https://157nym.github.io/media/posts/8/ITPR.png" class="type:primaryImage" alt="" /></p>
                
  <p>
    I.P.T.R is a solo game I made in just 3 days during my first year, for a Game Jam hosted by ICAN.
<br>
<br>The theme was Space Opera, and I handled everything — from game design and visuals to programming.
<br>
<br>Since it was my very first jam ever, and as a first year just starting out, things went south pretty quickly. It was a fun learning experience, but the game definitely didn’t get close to being playable.
<br>
<br>I was still getting familiar with Unity, so this project helped me understand the basics of the engine and start working with C#.
  </p>
